metadata.name: White Rabbit
metadata.description:
It was past the legal hours to be out in the city. Two offenders secretly meet up to make the exchange. Will you take the red pill or the blue 
pill?

"You cannot take too long to make your choice, the sirens are drawing nearer and we must make our ways." 

Take the red pill and you will awaken from the illusion and control society has created for us, take the blue pill and you will awaken in your bed, forgetting everything you have learned. 

People are afraid when their reality is shattered and not many people are ready to be awoken from their fabricated 'truths'. Are reality and truth worth pursuing? Or would you rather maintain your social constructs, unshaken and comfortable?

The sirens have stopped now, they are steps away, they are coming. 
Make your choice.
